<hr>

<p>Here's my personal opinion:<br>
While I don't think that Lion's scrollbars are ugly, I do think that people should be able to use whatever scrollbars they like, be that their OS's scrollbars, their browser's scrollbars, or a custom stylesheet. Generally, sites that override that without a very good reason end up just being annoying</p>


